data.description: This one of a kind residence boasts seven bedrooms and four bathrooms, awaiting your personalization. With ample space, the house offers a meticulously maintained interior, featuring a recently remodeled primary bathroom. Enjoy the convenience of a home office upstairs and a study downstairs.  An outstanding feature is the entertainment room, complete with a bar. Furthermore, the basement holds vast potential with its spaciousness, 10-foot ceilings, and numerous possibilities. Situated on a generous lot, this expansive ranch-style home presents breathtaking mountain views and resides in a peaceful cul-de-sac. Noteworthy is the property's oversized deck, perfect for outdoor relaxation, while the private deck off the main bedroom also provides stunning views.  The roof, less than 5 years old, ensures durability. Conveniently located near open spaces, trails, the light-rail and Standley Lake, this home invites outdoor exploration. Additionally, its proximity to Old Town Arvada, just 2 miles away, guarantees easy access to dining, shopping, and entertainment options, offering an ideal blend of convenience and leisure.
